<doc id="905826" wikidata="Q5464066" url="?curid=905826" title="Fogarty's Cove">
<text>Fogarty&#x27;s Cove is a 1977 folk music album by Stan Rogers. It was his first album, released by Barnswallow Records, which was then purchased by Stan Rogers and made into Fogarty&#x27;s Cove Records.

The CD was one of several Stan Rogers albums reissued in 2011 by Borealis Records. The reissued CDs featured completely new cover artwork.

